DTSTART:20260618T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:The world is dancing\, succumb to the mad rhythm of Argentine T
	ango! In this program\, you will be introduced to Tango fundamentals throu
	gh rhythms and learn about musicality\, connection\, basic patterns\, and 
	communication. You don’t need a partner or experience.\n\nhttps://www.levy
	parkhouston.org/events/argentine-tango-series-2/2026-06-18/\n\nFrom Levy P
	ark Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/argentine-tango-series-2/2026-06
